snippet.textDisplay:
What a waste....!!!
Imagine if Shuja himself would have sung this.. why didn't he?

Edit: more I listen to this more I am liking it like it grows on you. So I decided to put this to a test with best audio equipment available to me(no bragging!!) and I must say great job guys!!!
It takes a lot of hard work in the background to create a composition like this.
 Momina and Asim you both shine in this masterpiece within your own brilliant capabilities and once again hats off to Shuja for just an incredibly pleasant composition. 

This is going to stay in my most repeated songs for a while along with the original, even my 5 year old has started liking it (She doesn't have a choice anyway when buckled up in the back seat :D )
